  "Barbados":{ flag:"🇧🇧", capital:"Bridgetown", population:"280,000", language:"English", sport:"Cricket", fact:"Barbados has the highest per-capita consumption of rum in the world and was the origin of the rum trade — the island's Mount Gay distillery, founded in 1703, is the oldest working rum distillery on Earth." },
